
Learning Custom Bot with Static Page

https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/ai/greetings-visitor-engage-your-web-users-with-amazon-lex/


1. Build the Amazon lex chatbot

2.Set up Amazon Cognito
	Create a pool for static page and remark the poolid for it.

3. IAM > Roles > Cognito_bot_pool_Unauth_Role > 
	Attach the policies:
	AmazonLexRunBotsOnly
	AmazonPollyReadOnlyAccess 


4. Write the chatbox static page using poolId and Bot name

Successfully Done!!!!!

